data.description:
Peaceful country living in a quiet neighborhood located in a cul de sac and boasting over one acre of green land to enjoy the outdoors. This 2019 modern home with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms has spacious bedrooms and living area. The beautiful bright kitchen is large complete with appliances,  ample storage and a huge center island. Large picture windows complete with blinds make this home birght and airy. Prepare dinner while watching your family enjoy the outside on over one acre of open land.  
The primary bedroom is comfortable and roomy with a walk in closet and a primary bathroom with double sinks, plenty of counter space, a stand alone shower. Relax in the oversized tub underneath 2 huge windows with a view to the outdoors. 
The remaining 2 bedrooms  located on the opposite side of the house are spacious and share a bathroom.
The private walk in laundry room located conveniently off the kitchen peeks to the back porch and the large backyard.
Washer/dryer included, new storage shed can convey.
Refrigerator does not covey.
